{"tid":883484,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女大生趴桌遭襲胸　男大生：摸起來很舒服 圖","createTime":"2018-10-31T01:21:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T01:45:29.000Z","uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d8c582f083e1429f71a457e3ad0a3ef606a4cedf","tid":883484,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T01:21:08.000Z","msg":"年約20歲的姜姓男子出庭時否認襲胸，說他本來就對女同學有好感，也想追求她，女同學也未排斥，他認為兩人是在曖昧期，案發當天他坐在女同學背後，只是用手指點女同學背部，並沒襲胸或性騷擾。<br />\n但受害的女學生卻說，起初她趴在桌子上休息，姜男坐在他旁邊時就突然摸她胸部，她嚇一跳沒多說，但心裡並不開心，於是走出教室，之後請另名女同學坐她旁邊，結果姜男又坐到她背後，突然摸她背部，讓她覺得不舒服，決定提告。<br />\n檢方調閱兩人LINE對話紀錄，發現女學生事後曾傳訊質問姜男：「你又想襲胸嗎？」姜男竟回稱：「對啊！摸起來很舒服」，雖然姜男辯稱那是另一次發生的事，不是指當天在教室的狀況，但檢察官不採信，認為姜男襲胸、摸背涉犯性騷擾罪，將他起訴。（<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181031/1457195\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181031%2F1457195&d=QPwT%2ByELcvOQ3V%2B17dE42QhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=811128e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181031%2F1457195&h=db3a92f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181031/1457195</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181031/640_e923ad27caeb597b11be8927cb9fbd5a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181031%2F640_e923ad27caeb597b11be8927cb9fbd5a.jpg&h=4289c94d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180527/640_46415efeb305f2603cdc99d5f6580508.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180527%2F640_46415efeb305f2603cdc99d5f6580508.jpg&h=856b3003&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自己合上眼將圖合而為一"},{"pid":"b77fdf2867ec3d59022519695b48eb7d80c756b9","tid":883484